OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFailing NHS negligence     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsystem must change, say MPs
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A major reform of the way NHS clinical 
OL,6, negligence claims are handled in       
OL,7, England is needed, MPs say.            
OL,9,FThe House of Commons' Health and Social
OL,10,FCare Committee said the current system 
OL,11,Fwas too adversarial, leading to bitter 
OL,12,Fand long legal fights for patients.    
OL,14,FMore than #2bn a year is paid out on   
OL,15,Fclaims, but 25% goes to legal fees.    
OL,17,FAn independent body should be set up to
OL,18,Fadjudicate on cases and the need to    
OL,19,Fprove individual fault should be       
OL,20,Fscrapped, the cross-party group said.  
